metadata.name: Padmakshi
metadata.description:
Saraswati Ji is the goddess of all art forms and everything related to art. She is white & bright like the moon, wearing a garland of pearls. Her hand is adorned with the finest veena and the Vedas, suggesting that Saraswati holds all knowledge in her hands. She is believed to be held in reverence by Brahma, Vishnu & Shankar.

** Non-Animated High-resolution version is available for collectors; contact the artist via DM.
** Music/Vocals by Samarth Saxena, recorded in studios with pro musicians, exclusive to the Rebel Club's Diwali Collab, with 15+ artists.
